<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>K. H. 427</author>
<hymn_number>423</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Pathien lehkha ka ging chai,
 Isu thutak agen hi;
 Van zawtna lampi pen ahi,
 Vanah I kal thei ui.

[V2]
 Aw Bible! Aw Bible!
 Ka hun ngai, ka hun thalah;
 Aw Bible! Aw Bible!
 Pathien lehkhabu hi.

[V3]
 2. Pathien lungthim thuk umdan,
 Gitloh leh mihiem umdan;
 I damnau le a gen chiena,
 Thu lulpen ahi ie.

[V4]
 3. Isu, Bible a pha ie,
 Pathien thilpiek chuh ahi;
 Thih a thawhkitna thu a gen,
 Hinna thu chuh ahi.

[V5]
 4. Zana thaumei vak guolin,
 Na thu'n lungthim a salhvak;
 Go phapen sangin a lul zawi,
 Lunggil in vawp ingka.</lyrics>
<title>O BIBLE!</title>
</song>